    # I should see only the related release.
    # And the distribution directly associated.
    Then I should see the following tiles in the correct order:
      # Created in 8:08am.
      | IS protocol draft 2  |
      # Created in 8:02am.
      | IS protocol meet-up  |
      # Created in 8:01am.
      | IS protocol paper    |
      # Created in 7:59am.
